title: Seven Nations discography, plus members' solo records
description:
This torrent contains the following Albums from the band Seven Nations:

# Rain and Thunder (1994)
# Old Ground (1995)
# Big Dog (1996)
# Road Kill (Two Volume Live Set) (1998)
# The Factory (1999)
# The Pictou Sessions (2000)
# Seven Nations (2000)
# Live at the Palace Theater (2001)
# And Now It&#039;s Come to This (2002)
# Clan Na Gael: 10 Years On (2005)
# Thanks For Waiting (2005)

Plus solo records from current and past members:

# Kirk McLeod - So Piano (2003)
# Dan Stacey - Crank It (2003)
# Neil Anderson - Revenge of the Antipypr
# Full Circle - Irish Music in America, Volume 2 (Featuring Neil Anderson)
